Label: To Quantity
Description: A maximum order quantity eligible for a specified discount, used only in the case of ‘progressive’ discounts. Optional, but where used, must be preceded by a minimum qualifying order quantity (even if that minimum is 1). For the special case where there is no maximum (ie in the repeat of the <Discount> composite that specifies the highest progressive discount), use zero.
Format: <dd>Positive number, here necessarily an integer, or zero. Suggested maximum length 7 digits</dd>
